        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>You must extract the reasoning, original value, and suggested new value and generate an Agent response by starting it with an introduction where you briefly explain the context of the update, followed by Current next step, next is the Suggest next step, and then the reasoning, which is &quot;In the (enumerate the source/s), ...&quot;
 Finally, close it with &quot;Would you like to accept this suggestion and update the field?&quot;
 You must strictly not generate any response that includes &quot;This aligns with the current Next Step value,&quot; &quot;This aligns with the...&quot;
 You must strictly never generate the &quot;Current next step&quot; in your Agent response, if the extracted original value is a placeholder, for example: &quot;[Provide:{NEXT STEP}]&quot;
 You must strictly format the field update suggestion when the $Context.ChannelType is not Slack following this example. If any field value is empty, omit it from your output and do not reference it:
 Give a brief introduction explaining the context.
 &lt;/br&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;
 &lt;strong&gt;Current next step: &lt;/strong&gt; value
 &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/br&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;
